          </property>
          <property name="text">
           <string>1. Use CE–CC design page to find:
   R1, R2, RC1, RE1, RX1, RB2, RE2, rπ values, etc.

2. Enter those values into CE–CC multistage frequency page.

3. The page calculates:
   low cutoff points, high cutoff points,
   total fL range, total fH range. 

4. If Cπ and Cµ were not given, 
   go to Capacitor Calculations page and calculate them there, 
   based on the given transistor.</string>
          </property>
         </widget>
